	 <title>System.Sleep</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator stops the current process for the specified number of
		  milliseconds.</para> 
	 <example>
		  <title>Example</title>
		  <programlisting>Sleep(2000);</programlisting>
	 </example> 
